main event: A witness observed a white, round object in the sky over Kansas City, Missouri in 1965.
interesting points: The object appeared to dart to and fro, then disappear.
The object was described as fuzzy and blurred.
The witness believed the object could have been an aircraft reflecting city lights.
The witness estimated the object was moving at a speed of around 500 mph.
The witness was unable to get a good three-dimensional view of the object due to poor viewing conditions.
sighted object: a white, round object in the sky
